      <abstract id="aspace_98ecd6a37a4ab6867b3d27336b70856c" label="Abstract">The <emph render="italic">Black Sun</emph> Archive is a collection of correspondence and manuscripts sent to the poetry magazine, <emph render="italic">Black Sun</emph> which was edited by poet, Harvey Tucker.</abstract>
